  "raw_sections": [
    "Oh, thedepthof theriches",
    "And thewisdomandknowledgeofGod;",
    "How unsearchableare Hisjudgments;",
    "How untraceableare Hispaths.",
    "Forwho hasknown themindoftheLord,",
    "Orwho hasbeen Hiscounselor?",
    "Orwho hasfirst givento Him,",
    "Andit willberepaidtohim?",
    "Becauseout ofHim andthroughHim",
    "Andto Himareall things.",
    "ToHim bethegloryforever.Amen."
  ]
